%% Current State: Flight Test Process
flowchart TD
classDef gate fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#c0392b,color:#fff
classDef milestone fill:#2ecc71,stroke:#27ae60,color:#fff
classDef feedback fill:#f39c12,stroke:#e67e22,color:#fff
classDef process fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#90caf9,color:#1a237e
classDef artifact fill:#fff3bf,stroke:#ffcc02,color:#333
classDef external fill:#e0e0e0,stroke:#9e9e9e,color:#333

start([Need flight test]) --> plan[Plan test informally]
plan --> prep[Prep aircraft]
prep --> fly[Fly test event]
fly --> debrief[Debrief team]
debrief --> notes(Write notes)
notes --> share([Share results by email/chat])
share --> next((Next test or update))

class start,share external
class plan,prep,fly,debrief process
class notes artifact
class next milestone
